# Fast-Api-App

Minimal FastAPI starter project.

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e .[dev]
```

## Run

```bash
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
```

## Test

```bash
pytest
```
